### Teacher routes (used by /teacher and nested teacher views)

### Teacher dashboard stats
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get teacher's lessons (list)
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Create a lesson (teacher)
POST http://localhost:5173/lessons
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Przykładowa lekcja",
  "theme": "Grammar",
  "groupIds": [1]
}

### Edit lesson (teacher owner)
PUT http://localhost:5173/lessons/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "title": "Zaktualizowana lekcja",
  "theme": "Grammar",
  "groupIds": [1]
}

### Get lesson stats (teacher view)
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/lessons/1/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get lesson result for a student (teacher view)
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/lessons/1/students/1/result
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get teacher's students
GET http://localhost:5173/teacher/students
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


